name: NavsterHikes
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: where is navster
des: This is Navster's backpacking journal. It will provide to you the most recent trail update as he hikes different long trails across the United States, such as the Appalachian Trail, the Colorado Trail, the Pacific Crest Trail, and others. It's your easiest way to stay up-to-date with your local adventurer!
